Module downfall
Package net.dragondelve.ui.editor

Class MaterialsEditorController

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.dragondelve.downfall.ui.editor.MaterialsEditorController
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    StageController
    public final class MaterialsEditorController
extends java.lang.Object
implements StageController
    Controller class for the Materials Editor. It is responsible for the creation and editing of VisualMaterialTemplates in the current ruleset. Controls /fxml/editors/MaterialsEditor.fxml and is annotated with @FXML where it references that FXML file.
